events.text: Okay. Before I forget, let me give you a spare key for the apartment.
I'm not gonna be here during the day, so if you wanted to go out or something, you'll need it to unlock the door.
You hand Luma the spare key to the apartment.
Oh, thanks! Could you put it over there?
Luma points to the end of the coffee table in the room with her "stub".
You place it gently at the pointed out spot and continue your daily routine.
